array.note: p[j] is the period (time) of the jth product
np[i][j] is the number of products made at time j and required by customer i
r[i][t] is 1 iff the product made at time t concerns customer i
o[i][t] is 1 iff the stack is open for customer i at time t
aux_gb[i] is the ith auxiliary variable having been automatically introduced

allDifferent.note: all products are scheduled at different times

minimize.note: minimizing the number of stacks that are simultaneously open
